Mini Mental State Exam

Source: R/data.R
MMSE.Rd

Mini Mental State Exam data. More information is available at https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Usage

data(MMSE)

Format

A data frame with 14159 observations and 59 variables.

Source

https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Details

  • ORIGPROT character Original study protocol , with options: ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI3, ADNI4

  • COLPROT factor Study protocol of data collection , with factor levels: ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI3, ADNI4

  • PTID character Participant ID

  • RID numeric Participant roster ID Range value: 1, ..., 10664

  • VISCODE character Visit code

  • VISCODE2 character Translated visit code

  • VISDATE Assessment DATE when present; otherwise Registry EXAMDATE Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • DONE character Was assessment/procedure done?

    • ADNI3: 0=No;1=Yes

    • ADNI4: 0=No; 1=Yes

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • NDREASON character If No, reason not done

    • ADNI3: 1=Participant Unable for Cognitive Reasons;2=Participant Unable for Other Reasons (Physical, auditory, etc.);3=Participant/Study Partner Refused;7=Site Error;8=Other Reason;9=Unknown

    • ADNI4: 1=Participant Unable for Cognitive Reasons; 2=Participant Unable for Other Reasons (Physical, auditory, etc.); 3=Participant/Study Partner Refused; 7=Site Error; 8=Other Reason; 9=Unknown

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • SOURCE character Information Source

    • ADNI3: 1=Participant Visit;2=Telephone Call/Video Call

    • ADNI4: 1=Participant Visit; 2=Telephone Call/Video Call

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMDATE character Score (date)

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI3: 0=0 - Incorrect;1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMYEAR character Score (year)

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI3: 0=0 - Incorrect;1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMMONTH character Score (month)

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI3: 0=0 - Incorrect;1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMDAY character Score (day of the week)

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI3: 0=0 - Incorrect;1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMSEASON character Score (season)

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI3: 0=0 - Incorrect;1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMHOSPIT character Score (building)

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI3: 0=0 - Incorrect;1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMFLOOR character Score (floor)

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI3: 0=0 - Incorrect;1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMCITY character Score (city/town)

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI3: 0=0 - Incorrect;1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMAREA character Score (county)

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI3: 0=0 - Incorrect;1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMSTATE character Score (state)

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI3: 0=0 - Incorrect;1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • WORDLIST character Which list was used?

    • ADNI3: 1=Ball, Flag, Tree;2=Apple, Penny, Table

    • ADNI4: 1=Ball, Flag, Tree; 2=Apple, Penny, Table

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • WORD1 character Ball (alt: Apple)

    • ADNI3: 0=0 - Incorrect;1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • WORD2 character Flag (alt: Penny)

    • ADNI3: 0=0 - Incorrect;1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • WORD3 character Tree (alt: Table)

    • ADNI3: 0=0 - Incorrect;1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMTRIALS numeric 13a. Enter number of trials

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2: 1..6

    • ADNI3

  • MMD character 14. D 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • MML character 15. L 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMR character 16. R 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMO character 17. O 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMW character 18. W 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMLTR1 character Indicate 1st letter

  • MMLTR2 character Indicate 2nd letter

  • MMLTR3 character Indicate 3rd letter

  • MMLTR4 character Indicate 4th letter

  • MMLTR5 character Indicate 5th letter

  • MMLTR6 character Indicate 6th letter (if given) , with options: -, w, D, W, O, S, d, x, M

  • MMLTR7 character Indicate 7th letter (if given) , with options: -, _, x

  • WORLDSCORE numeric Score: World Backwards Range value: 0, ..., 5

  • WORD1DL character Ball (alt: Apple)

    • ADNI3: 0=0 - Incorrect;1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • WORD2DL character Flag (alt: Penny)

    • ADNI3: 0=0 - Incorrect;1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • WORD3DL character Tree (alt: Table)

    • ADNI3: 0=0 - Incorrect;1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMWATCH character What is this? [Point to a watch]

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI3: 0=0 - Incorrect;1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMPENCIL character What is this? [Point to a pencil or pen]

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI3: 0=0 - Incorrect;1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMREPEAT character No ifs, ands, or buts

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI3: 0=0 - Incorrect;1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMHAND character Takes in right hand

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI3: 0=0 - Incorrect;1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMFOLD character Folds in half

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI3: 0=0 - Incorrect;1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMONFLR character Puts on floor

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI3: 0=0 - Incorrect;1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMREAD character Close your eyes

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI3: 0=0 - Incorrect;1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMWRITE character Please write a sentence

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI3: 0=0 - Incorrect;1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMDRAW character Please copy this design

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI3: 0=0 - Incorrect;1=1 - Correct

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI4: 0=0 - Incorrect; 1=1 - Correct

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMSCORE numeric MMSE TOTAL SCORE

    • ADNI1, ADNI2, ADNI3: 0..30

    • ADNIGO, ADNI4

  • ID numeric Record ID Range value: 10, ..., 186199

  • SITEID numeric Site ID Range value: 1, ..., 941

  • USERDATE User Create Date Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • USERDATE2 User Last Modify Date Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • DD_CRF_VERSION_LABEL character CRF Version Label , with options: v1

  • LANGUAGE_CODE character Language Code e=English Decoded Value: Yes

  • HAS_QC_ERROR character Has Quality Check Error 0=Does not have QC error or QC error has been approved; 1=Has QC error Decoded Value: Yes

  • update_stamp POSIXct: YYY-MM-DD
